
         
         <p>This is about the first version of <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">show-font.el</code>. I just pushed the
changes to show-font.git and elpa.git, so expect the new package to be available in the coming hours. Below are some screen shots and the release notes for version <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">0.1.0</code>.</p>

<h2>Sources</h2>

